                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَهۡدِيٓ إِلَى ٱلرُّشۡدِ﴾: يَدْعُو إِلى الحقِّ.</h2>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "72:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تَعَٰلَىٰ جَدُّ رَبِّنَا﴾: عَلَتْ وارْتَفَعَتْ عَظَمَةُ رَبِّنا وَجَلَالُهُ، وَأمْرُهُ، وقُدْرَتُهُ.</p>\n<h2>﴿صَٰحِبَةٗ﴾: زَوْجةً.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "72:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
